This is a custom distribution of the Bullet Physics Library, version 2.76.

This distribution includes a custom CMake-based build system tailored to fit in
the Athena Game Framework. Only the library is distributed (ie. there is no demo
application or tool included).


License
-------

Bullet's license is unchanged: this library is released under the ZLib License.

The license of Bullet is contained in the file 'LICENSE'.


Compilation
-----------

It is recommended to compile the library in a separate folder. Here's how I do it:

  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ cmake ..
  $ make
